 As DJs, Stoneface & Terminal are famed for their high-energy edged style. With the power of their DJ-sets they have the makings to fascinate and the crowd all around the world.
 They played gigs in the USA, Malaysia, Mexico and Australia and its always a great experience to see these two best friends perform behind the decks.
 In June of 2007 Stoneface & Terminal released their first artist album called Wide Range.
 Further Stoneface & Terminal made special versions of their known tracks like Another Day, Super Nature or Drowning Sunlight. The musical style varies between relaxing tunes, vocal based songs and energy loaded club tracks.
Stoneface & Terminal "10 Years" THE album on Euphonic Records incl. the singles, 2015 reworks, NET SON remix, Kyau & Albert remix
